japan consum price unchang in februari japan 's consum price index ( base 1985 ) wa unchang at 99.7 in februari from a month earlier , the govern 's manag and coodin agenc said . the index show a 0.4 pct drop in januari . the februari index wa down one pct from a year earlier for the third consecut year-on-year drop . in januari , the index fell 1.1 pct from a year earlier , the first drop of over one pct sinc a 1.3 pct drop in septemb 1958. in februari petrol price increas but winter cloth price stay low and veget price fell . the februari year on year fall wa due to lower veget , fuel oil , petrol , electr and ga price , and despit higher hous , educ , footwear and cloth cost . the unadjust consum price index for the tokyo area ( base 1985 ) in mid-march rose 0.4 pct from a month earlier to 100.6 , reflect higher veget price . the index fell 0.3 pct year on year , the third consecut yearli drop , reflect lower food and util cost .